WordPress packaged for CaaS Express Trial

- it includes the Wordpress WebApp + mariaDB / MemCached with Persistent Volume
- all dependencies have been packaged to its charts folder
- all required images have been available from Pulp registry:

  - image:
    registry: gl3-pulpnode.gl-hpe.local
    repository: wordpress
    tag: 5.9.3-debian-11-r0

  - image:
    registry: gl3-pulpnode.gl-hpe.local
    repository: mariadb
    tag: 10.6.8-debian-11-r0

  - image:
    registry: gl3-pulpnode.gl-hpe.local
    repository: memcached
    tag: 1.6.15-debian-11-r0
